Chelsea Hires Porto’s Andre Villas-Boas as Coach on Three-Year Contract

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-06-22T09:47:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/chelsea-hires-porto-s-andre-villas-boas-as-coach-on-three-year-contract.html
Chelsea hired Andre Villas-Boas as
coach after payment of a reported 15 million-euro ($21.6
million) fee to release him from his contract at Porto.  He’s been appointed on a three-year contract, Chelsea said
on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
